com.apigee.flow.execution
Class ExecutionResult

java.lang.Object
  com.apigee.flow.execution.ExecutionResult

public class ExecutionResult
extends java.lang.Object

 Represents a result of the execution.

 If there is an error, the execution instance can populate the desired error
 response content and the error response headers. These will be sent back
 to the client appropriately.
